系統設定中把瀏海「隱藏」起來。所謂的「隱藏」就是把整個狀態欄都變成固定的黑色，這樣就可以把瀏海拉成一個直線。<br />\n￼大家在使用華為 P20 或 P20 Pro 時，在系統設定中就可以找到這個，不過我就認為這是一個自欺欺人的方法，要用瀏海屏就是要更多的屏佔比視覺效果，但如果這樣隱藏起來還不如一開始直接不設計成瀏海屏不是更好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/205606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F205606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d74602a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">OLED，等睇燒印</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"我都有睇過其他人話咁會好易有印<br />\n但唔明點解，佢果個位長期黑色都會燒印？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"d 字係白色"},{"pid":"317e70af73f1a76c8de1f76519b1d4a0873a3e05","tid":646940,"uid":152244,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"其實樓主有無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f8bb61905b5c5d769bd0ef55c2cb94ec8812bf","tid":646940,"uid":181065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c44150c74c2012cb964036018db7fc274caf68d","tid":646940,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe503a4c2cb1660c83750debcb7054417f9c9ec","tid":646940,"uid":36822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c3100b62206cbd4394ceb1e17f4a0c768d63f69","tid":646940,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"oled全黑都燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"寫文果個根本就為反而反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"幫iPhone洗白<img src=\"/